sentence: In early trading on Tuesday, shares of Visa (V) topped the list of the day's best performing Dow Jones Industrial Average components, trading up 1.1%.
Year to date, Visa registers a 37.7% gain.
And the worst performing Dow component thus far on the day is Home Depot (HD), trading down 5.4%.
Home Depot is showing a gain of 31.6% looking at the year to date performance.
Two other components making moves today are Walgreens Boots Alliance (WBA), trading down 0.6%, and Merck & Co (MRK), trading up 0.7% on the day.
